{"tid":1993384,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港島總共有6席，有以下候選人。","createTime":"2020-04-28T17:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T03:03:40.000Z","uid":61161,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b83d179be42a7739ab016dc4d2d74c3c16e8a6d6","tid":1993384,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"睇完個名單，真係唉咗一唉...<br />\n<br />\n香港島總共有6席，有以下候選人。<br />\n<br />\n2016立法會選舉香港島候選名單 : <br />\n<br />\n1號 黃梓謙 (民主思路)<br />\n2號 劉嘉鴻、袁彌明 (人民力量)<br />\n3號 葉劉淑儀、陳家珮、李文龍、謝子祺、洪龍荃、王政芝 (新民黨)<br />\n4號 何秀蘭、麥德正、鄭司律 (工黨)<br />\n5號 張國鈞、鍾樹根、鍾嘉敏、麥謝巧玲、丁江浩、王志鍾 (民建聯)<br />\n6號 詹培忠 (獨立)<br />\n7號 鄭錦滿、鍾琬媛 (熱血公民)<br />\n8號 羅冠聰 (香港眾志)<br />\n9號 沈志超 (獨立)<br />\n10號 王維基 (獨立)<br />\n11號 徐子見 (獨立)<br />\n12號 司馬文 (獨立)<br />\n13號 許智峯、單仲偕 (民主黨)<br />\n14號 陳淑莊、鄭達鴻 (公民黨)<br />\n15號 郭偉强、吳秋北、何毅淦、呂鴻賓、陳榮恩 (工聯會)<br />\n<br />\n選票分佈<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;新民黨&nbsp;(16.13%)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;香港眾志&nbsp;(13.49%)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;工聯會&nbsp;(12.20%)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;民主黨&nbsp;(11.29%)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;民建聯&nbsp;(10.93%)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;公民黨&nbsp;(9.40%)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;熱血公民&nbsp;(5.99%)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;工黨&nbsp;(5.15%)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;民主思路&nbsp;(2.66%)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;人民力量/社民連&nbsp;(1.93%)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;其他 (10.83%)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目標4席可以嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa22195f75669de6f4bc3661ca6afd98f3e3f8e","tid":1993384,"uid":258731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:32:27.000Z","msg":"絕對可以<br />\n但係前提係要解決咗支那01<br />\n<br />\n－－－<br />\n<br />\n【打柒支那01】共派政黨民建聯得分上升8% 黨媒01是背後元兇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1993353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1993353</a><br />\n<br />\n支那01帶風向同滲透已經延伸到連登外面 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家訓醒未</span></span><br />\n立法會選戰 連登仔第一個考驗：打柒支那01<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/LD7dnxE.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知道點解今次中共病毒疫情，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共派政黨</span></span></strong>，特別係<span style=\"color: blue;\">民建聯</span>，民意得分直線上升???<br />\n答案：係因為支那01係背後緊搞鬼！！<br />\n『<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/chi/press-release/2020/20200428-chi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fchi%2Fpress-release%2F2020%2F20200428-chi&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=5d0516ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/chi/press-release/2020/20200428-chi</a><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">民研計劃於四月中由真實訪問員以隨機抽樣電話訪問方式，分兩階段成功訪問了506和500名香港居民。最新政治團體民望調查顯示，對比七個月前，以熟悉程度計，首3位最多巿民認識的政治團體分別是民建聯、民主黨和公民黨，而民協則取代民陣重新上榜。論支持度評分，香港眾志以43.1分首次奪得首位；第二至六位是民主黨、民協、人民力量、公民黨和社民連，分別得42.9、41.6、40.0、39.4及39.0分；自由黨、民建聯、工聯會和新民黨分別排第七至十位，得37.7、35.2、32.0及29.7分。市民對排名首五位政治團體的平均分為41.4分，而首十位則為38.1分。公民黨的評分較七個月前顯著下跌5.7分，是其於2006年上榜以來的新低，</span></em>而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯則顯著上升8.4分。</span></span>』<br />\n<br />\n2020.04.24 損人不利己並非為政之道<br />\nWHAT THE FUCK<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n刻意放大公民黨郭榮鏗 「阻住晒」「影響民生，議會運作」的負面形象<br />\n堅守議會 減慢赤化速度 阻止23條立法絕口不提<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200425/330694038183350272.jpeg/xOIvOti9hUrUMpiVpHqQNKNjKr1_oTUdPeuMQT3rjEE?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200425%2F330694038183350272.jpeg%2FxOIvOti9hUrUMpiVpHqQNKNjKr1_oTUdPeuMQT3rjEE%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=6337beae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔該你哋班連登仔唔撚好再share 01 news，唔好再被佢帶風向<br />\n搞鳩我哋香港人咁撚耐 支那01呢條數香港人未同你計 <br />\n一定要打撚柒支那01"},{"pid":"5fe48e87b92c860c17b177e6dad0c9a9672f80da","tid":1993384,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:32:27.000Z","msg":"會唔會太理想？<br />\n3:3 第4席搵中間保守好喎"},{"pid":"0b30707c6b454f09a384ee031f981c5cd7b32c4b","tid":1993384,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:37:28.000Z","msg":"【立法會選舉】港島初選見雛形 倡每名選民有4票 10人表態參選<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200327/A6Y2FV7BZYWPGCOPTFGCQMPAQU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200327%2FA6Y2FV7BZYWPGCOPTFGCQMPAQU%2F&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=f0f155d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200327%2FA6Y2FV7BZYWPGCOPTFGCQMPAQU%2F&h=f9a0b259\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200327/A6Y2FV7BZYWPGCOPTFGCQMPAQU/</a><br />\n<br />\n來自傳統政黨的計有民主黨現任議員許智峯、接棒陳淑莊的公民黨鄭達鴻、上屆當選但被DQ的香港眾志羅冠聰；「單頭」人士則有灣仔區議會主席楊雪盈、區議員梁晃維、彭卓棋、司馬文、徐子見、維多利亞協會周世傑及2047香港監察錢志健。<br />\n<br />\n4隊，thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9e02a701f0806584d43dd8f4e8a25d9b023063","tid":1993384,"uid":217451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T17:42:42.000Z","msg":"最理想係出4隊 分得平均攞4席"},{"pid":"6dc2ebec47ad0e2a54ffc1e2d0c6e0477acaa590","tid":1993384,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T18:13:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">[緊急] 5月2日截止！選民登記自動波填表機(懶人專用)：</span><a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/\" data-sr-ur